@host = http://localhost:5194

### Valid Order (should be accepted and processed)
POST {{host}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "C001",
  "items": [
    { "sku": "ITEM-1", "quantity": 2, "unitPrice": 50.0 },
    { "sku": "ITEM-2", "quantity": 1, "unitPrice": 25.0 }
  ],
  "totalAmount": 125.0
}

###

### Invalid Order (should fail simple validation on API)
POST {{host}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "",
  "items": [],
  "totalAmount": 100.0
}

###

### Invalid Order (should fail domain validation and move to error queue)
POST {{host}}/api/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "customerId": "CUST-5678",
  "items": [
    { "sku": "ITEM-3", "quantity": 1, "unitPrice": 100.0 }
  ],
  "totalAmount": 100.0
}

###

### Get total count of all orders
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders
Accept: application/json

###

### Get count of pending orders
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders?status=pending
Accept: application/json

###

### Get count of processed orders
GET http://localhost:8080/api/orders?status=processed
Accept: application/json
